Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.97,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(364,358)}Activity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.51,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, {\alpha&HFF&}weren't these meetings supposed to be fortnightly? Seems they're getting more frequent than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.37,0:00:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, weren't these meetings supposed to be fortnightly? Seems they're getting more frequent than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've received a report from Coil which claims that Amane Misa may know L.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.10,0:00:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to his report, {\alpha&HFF&}"Amane Misa was questioned by L", but... here is where the problems arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to his report, "Amane Misa was questioned by L", {\alpha&HFF&}but... here is where the problems arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to his report, "Amane Misa was questioned by L", but... here is where the problems arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Based on what we know so far, it's fair to say that Amane idolizes Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, Yoshida Productions are pressing the Yotsuba Group to use her as a campaign girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I propose that the Yotsuba Group employ Amane in a commercial and utilize this opportunity to find out more about L."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I'm not entirely satisfied with this plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? {\alpha&HFF&}Sounds like a good plan to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? Sounds like a good plan to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, what Ooi means is that Coil is the one who's supposed to be uncovering L's identity, yet he has entrusted this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The original contract was for him to reveal L's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Coil should be present at this meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida-san, {\alpha&HFF&}I thought the original agreement was that you'd avoid calling me unless absolutely necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida-san, I thought the original agreement was that you'd avoid calling me unless absolutely necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this urgent?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. {\alpha&HFF&}If that's the case, I've got an excellent idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. If that's the case, I've got an excellent idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the meeting is over and I'm finally home, there's still criminals to take care of...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being Kira is hectic business...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's about to get interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt, Amane Misa was the second Kira and was caught by L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that she escaped in that situation can only mean that she relinquished her ownership of the Note and lost her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just too good an opportunity to pass up...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take Amane Misa as my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money, {\alpha&HFF&}power, and a beautiful wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money, power, {\alpha&HFF&}and a beautiful wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money, power, and a beautiful wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the envy of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're married, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll spend plenty of money on her life insurance policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're married, I'll spend plenty of money on her life insurance policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, {\alpha&HFF&}this degenerate wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, this degenerate wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, hide the notebook in the usual place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the only thing I can do for Misa... {\alpha&HFF&}is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the only thing I can do for Misa... is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's take it from the next part...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-san, {\alpha&HFF&}you went to Tokyo specifically hoping to meet Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-san, you went to Tokyo specifically hoping to meet Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-san, {\alpha&HFF&}I know the line sucks, but try not to overreact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-san, I know the line sucks, but try not to overreact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaa? This is what's known as credible acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, let's just try this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine, Mr. Ryuuzaki Director Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't start taking this seriously, you'll be feeling my foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-{\alpha&HFF&}Misa-Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Misa-Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face looks strained. Just "Misa" is fine, Mochii.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cut out for this... {\alpha&HFF&}but this is one of my duties too, and will aid in catching Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cut out for this... but this is one of my duties too, and will aid in catching Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mochii?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's interview with the Yotsuba Group is of course an opportunity for you to appear in their commercials,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's also a part of our undercover investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to tell me that, I already know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you better not mess up either. {\alpha&HFF&}Remember, you're supposed to be a super-energetic manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you better not mess up either. Remember, you're supposed to be a super-energetic manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! {\alpha&HFF&}I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Misa-Misa's manager, Moji Kan'ichi, also known as Mochii.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooi-san, Shimura-san, nice to see the both of you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Misa-Misa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mochii can really pull some tricks when he needs to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and prepare the celebrations for when you land this commercial!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cut out for this... am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe we've met before, have we, Misa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm John Wallace, the main adviser of the Advertising Department. It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let me get straight to the point and be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The decision to hire you to be in our commercials has more or less already been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before we seal the deal, there's just one more thing I'd like to have confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've taken the liberty of doing some investigation into your background;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems that you idolize Kira for killing the thieves that murdered your parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that you went to Tokyo specifically hoping to meet Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}Who... did you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who... did you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't reveal our sources, but our information is accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even your entire face screams "busted".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coil... I had no idea that he'd found out so much already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... {\alpha&HFF&}there's still something that you're hiding from us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... there's still something that you're hiding from us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something you wouldn't want the public to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the point where I've got to start sweating and pause for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Amane Misa was restrained by L". {\alpha&HFF&}I'd like to hear the truth straight from your own mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Amane Misa was restrained by L". I'd like to hear the truth straight from your own mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to have the Yotsuba campaign girl turn out to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed. Please be honest with us regarding this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}I understand... I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I understand... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I understand... I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true I was restrained... {\alpha&HFF&}but I didn't know it was L's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true I was restrained... but I didn't know it was L's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked about Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}but I'm not the second Kira, and they realized that I had no connection with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked about Kira, but I'm not the second Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}and they realized that I had no connection with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked about Kira, but I'm not the second Kira, and they realized that I had no connection with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you manage to see the face of the person restraining you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was blindfolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you must have heard their voice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But their voice was coming out of some speakers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, {\alpha&HFF&}this seems more like an interrogation than an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, this seems more like an interrogation than an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you planning to keep this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, it's true that we may have been going off on a bit of a tangent there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... {\alpha&HFF&}would it be okay for me to go to the toilet too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... would it be okay for me to go to the toilet too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so nerve-racking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But so far it seems to be going well... I've got to keep doing my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even by touching this scrap of paper, her lost memories won't return... {\alpha&HFF&}but at least Misa will be able to see me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even by touching this scrap of paper, her lost memories won't return... but at least Misa will be able to see me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What is this?! A ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?! {\alpha&HFF&}A ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?! A ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}right now you're in a dangerous situation where you could be killed by members of the Yotsuba Group at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, right now you're in a dangerous situation where you could be killed by members of the Yotsuba Group at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to come and tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Calm down"? {\alpha&HFF&}This ghost is much more likely to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Calm down"? This ghost is much more likely to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your ally, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... {\alpha&HFF&}ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Misa-Misa is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should at least have made her wear a wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that it's a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kira prior to my detention and the current Kira... {\alpha&HFF&}they're definitely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kira prior to my detention and the current Kira... they're definitely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The current Kira is killing off absolutely anyone who's been broadcast as a murderer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those who had no murderous intent... those who killed unintentionally... and those with mitigating circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they were never judged by the previous Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:08:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was Kira, I'd also judge in such a discerning way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The basis of the previous Kira's judgments are terrifyingly close to my own ideals...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comparing myself to Kira? There's clearly something wrong with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Light currently doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that you're not a stalker, {\alpha&HFF&}but you don't even remotely resemble a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that you're not a stalker, but you don't even remotely resemble a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I'm a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was once a time when we worked inseparably together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you're saying... I don't understand any of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa has met you?! {\alpha&HFF&}Light is Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa has met you?! Light is Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you write a person's name in it, {\alpha&HFF&}the person whose name was written will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you write a person's name in it, the person whose name was written will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using that Note, {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami Light passed judgment on criminals and became widely known as "Kira".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using that Note, Yagami Light passed judgment on criminals and became widely known as "Kira".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you held the same power as Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}No, a power even greater than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you held the same power as Kira. No, {\alpha&HFF&}a power even greater than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you held the same power as Kira. No, a power even greater than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using that power you were able to successfully approach Kira, in other words, Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light is Kira? {\alpha&HFF&}And Misa is the second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light is Kira? And Misa is the second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. {\alpha&HFF&}Or more accurately, you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. Or more accurately, {\alpha&HFF&}you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. Or more accurately, you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the current situation should all be a part of Light's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}he's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... he's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still love Light enough to die for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami-san, you're the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know everything about Misa! {\alpha&HFF&}I'll believe everything you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know everything about Misa! I'll believe everything you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... {\alpha&HFF&}I love him... to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I love him... {\alpha&HFF&}to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I love him... to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that Light was Kira, and Misa was Kira, that we both were Kira together... {\alpha&HFF&}that's truly fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that Light was Kira, and Misa was Kira, that we both were Kira together... that's truly fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never change, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I doubt that those feelings you have for Light will ever change either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So from now on, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll accept that your happiness lies in being with Light, and supporting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So from now on, I'll accept that your happiness lies in being with Light, and supporting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Shinigami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Presently, the current Kira is a disgusting lowlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling what he might do. {\alpha&HFF&}Be careful of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling what he might do. Be careful of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for any human who works for Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just trust Light, and let him handle it his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. {\alpha&HFF&}All Misa has got to do is act natural, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. All Misa has got to do is act natural, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you return to the interview, {\alpha&HFF&}you should be able to tell who Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you return to the interview, you should be able to tell who Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be especially wary of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for taking so long in the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even fixed my make-up in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you return from the toilet, the man sitting in front of me will be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person sitting in front of Rem is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi is Kira?! {\alpha&HFF&}It couldn't get any worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi is Kira?! It couldn't get any worse...
Comment: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-Misa is late...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew... I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yotsuba has decided to employ Misa in a multi-platform advertising campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? {\alpha&HFF&}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave them both my phone number and my e-mail address, and already three out of the seven have contacted me in private and asked me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I just need to accept their offers and begin investigating them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going according to the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that plan has been cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! It's all gone so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This method places you in too much danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell you not to do the commercial, {\alpha&HFF&}but from now on, you'll deny that you were the second Kira and were restrained by L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell you not to do the commercial, but from now on, you'll deny that you were the second Kira and were restrained by L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be guarded by Mogi-san, and you'll only work in your capacity as a "campaign girl".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bu--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light says so, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Misa is tired and she needs to be on location early tomorrow, so she's off to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:13:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for worrying about me, Light... {\alpha&HFF&}but I've thought of an excellent plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for worrying about me, Light... but I've thought of an excellent plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely help you, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light? {\alpha&HFF&}You want to sleep with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light? You want to sleep with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. {\alpha&HFF&}We can do that after Kira is caught, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. We can do that after Kira is caught, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to get so embarrassed, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be embarrassed, Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you taking it so seriously, Light-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a wrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm allowed to use the bathroom in this hospital, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! {\alpha&HFF&}Off you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Off you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait here a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai! Good job at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Mori-chan, that nurse's outfit really suits you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That went smoothly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I knew you would have an amazing car!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, I'll take you for a ride anytime. No, I'll just buy you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, that nurse's outfit looks great, Misa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's on a date...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi Kyousuke... {\alpha&HFF&}since we had that reception... he has persistently messaged and asked me out... that dirty old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:15:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi Kyousuke... since we had that reception... he has persistently messaged and asked me out... that dirty old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:58.90,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-chan, you're just my type...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.59,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Higuchi! Stop trying to get in before anyone else can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's truly horrible that Kira has to be someone like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-chan, you fancy getting something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not planning to take me anywhere dubious are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if you do try anything funny, Misa can kill people, so she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking, Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this something Yagami Light has told you to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. She must be attempting to tell me that if it comes down to it, I have to kill Higuchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so funny, Misa-chan. You can kill people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, because Misa is... {\alpha&HFF&}the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, because Misa is... the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-{\alpha&HFF&}No way. Even if this girl used to be the second Kira, she can't still be, can she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way. {\alpha&HFF&}Even if this girl used to be the second Kira, she can't still be, can she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way. Even if this girl used to be the second Kira, she can't still be, can she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should have no memory of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to lie just because you're wary of me, Misa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually quite the gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Misa has no interest in showing proof that she's the second Kira to anyone but Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll only show it to Kira? {\alpha&HFF&}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll only show it to Kira? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa's dream is to become Kira's wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm absolutely certain that Kira needs Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the incidents at Sakura TV, it's evident that the second Kira has the Shinigami's Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is true, I've got to keep her by my side, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try a test...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since I'm Kira, you'd better marry me, Misa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... {\alpha&HFF&}Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... Yeah, {\alpha&HFF&}really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proof! We should show each other proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. {\alpha&HFF&}It's far too dangerous to show anyone that you have the ability to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. It's far too dangerous to show anyone that you have the ability to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? {\alpha&HFF&}If Misa thought someone was Kira, she'd offer them proof of her own initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? If Misa thought someone was Kira, she'd offer them proof of her own initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless someone makes the first move, nothing will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, kill someone then. {\alpha&HFF&}I could be Kira you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, kill someone then. I could be Kira you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, {\alpha&HFF&}but I only kill bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, but I only kill bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... {\alpha&HFF&}"Bad" people, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... "Bad" people, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaneboshi Ginzou. {\alpha&HFF&}President of a large consumer financing company.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaneboshi Ginzou. President of a large consumer financing company.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A notorious villain that collects what he's owed through cruel methods. In some cases, he's forced people to pay out of their own life insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be able to check instantly if he's dead or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to make a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can you face that way for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, {\alpha&HFF&}you want me to kill Kaneboshi Ginzou, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, you want me to kill Kaneboshi Ginzou, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, Higuchi will believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.10,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz12.845\pos(196,277)}Kaneboshi Ginzou
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. He should be dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Higuchi from Yotsuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The president has just collapsed and stopped breathing! This will have to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She killed the person I specified, right here and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless she has the power, it would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That decides it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm Kira, you'll marry me, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}Why are you looking so serious all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you looking so serious all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to go home to kill, you understand that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's no good. It could merely be a trick to get Misa to go back to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! {\alpha&HFF&}Why don't you try and stop the judging of the criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Why don't you try and stop the judging of the criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really are Kira, you should be able to manage that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when Misa tells you to, you can begin judging them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe you if that happens, {\alpha&HFF&}since only Kira should be able to control the judging of criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe you if that happens, since only Kira should be able to control the judging of criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Nice idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kira. So in order to make you believe me, I'll stop judging criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once you realize that I am Kira, we're getting married!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, as you can all hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi is Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this we know Kira's identity, {\alpha&HFF&}and the judging of criminals that the Chief was so worried about will end too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this we know Kira's identity, and the judging of criminals that the Chief was so worried about will end too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing, Misa-Misa!
